results.title: Cover #50220
results.description: The first phenomenal issue! The next generation of mutant heroes begins their training now! Who is the energy-draining Emplate, and what is his connection to M?

results.title: Cover #50222
results.description: Generation X tries to figure out who the mysterious mutant Penance really is, and Gateway isn’t talking. Is the razor-sharp newcomer friend or foe?

results.title: Cover #50224
results.description: Penance is on the loose and there’s only one mutant who can stop her: Chamber!

results.title: Cover #50226
results.description: A very Generation X Christmas! When a disfigured child takes a teacher and his students hostage, it’s up to Generation X to save the class from the boy and from Orphan-Maker!

results.title: Cover #50228
results.description: Emma Frost has been kidnapped by the deadly Gene Nation!  Will her young trainees be strong enough to save her from these fearsome foes?

results.title: Cover #50230
results.description: Emma Frost and Generation X combat the substantial new threat that is Gene Nation.  Elsewhere, Chamber comforts Husk in a time of need, and the two grow closer.

results.title: Cover #50232
results.description: Banshee is haunted by nightmares from his time as an Interpol agent, and Emma Frost is listening in!  Meanwhile, The Gen X kids try to cope with each other and the new additions Artie and Leech.

results.title: Cover #50234
results.description: Cassidy Keep has disappeared! When Synch and Chamber get sucked into the same dimension as Banshee's home, it's up to the rest of Generation X to bring them back.

results.title: Cover #50236
results.description: Generation X vs. a fire-breathing dragon!

results.title: Cover #50238
results.description: Banshee lies near death as Emma Frost tries to save him. What thoughts lurk in the minds of dying men?

results.title: Cover #50240
results.description: Omega Red has taken out all of Generation X!  Except for Chamber, that is!  Will the young lone mutant be able to defeat such a powerful enemy?
